標題: 電信自由化政策法規與經營問題之研究A Study on the policy and management issues in telecommunications liberalization
作者: 何定為Ho Ting Wei曾繁藤Tseng Fan Tung傳播研究所
關鍵字: 電信自由化;電信政策;解除管制;民營化;Telecommunications liberalization;Telecommunications Policy; Deregulation;Privatization
公開日期: 1993
摘要: 本研究選定電信自由化議題,從政策法規的角度出發,探討台灣電信改革的
實然與應然.而改製後的電信公司面對著陌生的新市場體制,其經營概念與
方法的變遷,亦為本研究的探討主題.
This study on telecommunication searches for explanations for
the telecommunications reform in Taiwan and makes suggestions
on what the decision-making party should do for a policy regu-
lation point of view.
URI: http://140.113.39.130/cdrfb3/record/nctu/#NT820374007http://hdl.handle.net/11536/57797
